channel.title: Just did my Star Struck audition
channel.description:
I just did my Star Struck singing audition (Sang Hallelujah), and it went perfectly. The judges seemed happy and mesmorized during the performance, so i hope i get in.
If so i'll be singing 2+ songs over 3 nights on TV and in front of hundreds of people in a live audience. *squeal*
Yeh.. So just thought i'd let you know that. Since my nerves are only just now shaking off. I recorded the backing track myself because i couldn't find a proper one, and so now they know i play guitar and may up my chances more.
http://www.starstruck.nsw.edu.au/
<3 Kane.
